d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8889dba7336da5bfde304ea6a55579f35e5ce2b","tid":237114,"uid":76487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔好買1.5呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係咁無力？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身成個設計都偏柔, 2.0 唔開sport mode 都好乖, 1.5 唔敢想像<br />\n<br />\n同埋1.5 副engine 迨速偏高, 震d 嘈d (係維修中心試過)<br />\n<br />\n如果當腳車出出入入, 1.5 當然無任何問題, 係慢d, 但後覺較實用。2.0 有馬力好玩些少</blockquote><br />\n同其他1500車比呢？<br />\n例如spade jazz sienta<br />\n我以為有6at會好力d tim"},{"pid":"34f31ce6ffc846f7564fa3c81d9d10209b32faff","tid":237114,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>08年既mazda6 會唔會好多野整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無野整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53c8b1da5c9700a49222fe9fc2022abf2581136","tid":237114,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我會揀Mazda 2</blockquote><br />\n同價位我會要 Polo，始終差個 turbo爽好多，長渣就梗係 Mazda 3，仲一定要 Soul Red <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsoul red<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b93753ff25e0034581ed725f96de1f473976e36","tid":237114,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"比30買a3 sedan啦，又型，1.4 有150匹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c40bc04a053a724df3c395311684b45ee2e73b","tid":237114,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比30買a3 sedan啦，又型，1.4 有150匹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整鳩死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b420575ff42c5a7116743a9aae9abff6ba9a82ae","tid":237114,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比30買a3 sedan啦，又型，1.4 有150匹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整鳩死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整d咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643a0fbec222fc15461c5383e77924c4eac33299","tid":237114,"uid":50899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"新車30?  但係咪有保養架？ <br />\n其實老豆好想買歐洲車，如果呢個價真係想睇睇<br />\n同埋想問下大家我禁左寶馬個網，佢有d promotion price 好似平d , 但係咪都係正常一手野黎架？"},{"pid":"fdb26fda98a21135bdd21c37aadf80e9d3d55ce1","tid":237114,"uid":106945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"又黎加多少少系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係鍾意3 sedan, 1500cc 車唔好對馬力大要求<br />\n<br />\n唔加i-Plus, 簡簡單單, 本身既設備同內籠都ok<br />\n<br />\n不過都係果句, 試車作準<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同價位Golf 既隔音一定好過Mazda 3<br />\n<br />\n品牌Mazda 一定輸比VW Audi<br />\n要turbo 無turbo, 最慳油又唔係佢<br />\n<br />\n但我本人揸左幾個月好滿意, 有駕駛樂趣<br />\n<br />\n始終車係自己揸, 試過鍾唔鍾意自己決定"},{"pid":"0b1ae75f451a5d3406fef1aed4cae182acdcae29","tid":237114,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新車30?  但係咪有保養架？ <br />\n其實老豆好想買歐洲車，如果呢個價真係想睇睇<br />\n同埋想問下大家我禁左寶馬個網，佢有d promotion price 好似平d , 但係咪都係正常一手野黎架？</blockquote><br />\n309000好似，全新車，有保養，1.4牌費平，150匹馬力行街完全夠用，講真揸出黎，a3個款真係屌打mazda 3<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOH8KE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOH8KE3.jpg&h=3130d060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/132425_8530f43ef4c52247cbe6e27a901baa66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k